## Observability stack (docker-compose)

`docker compose up` now also brings:
- **Prometheus** on host port `19091` — remote-write receiver fed by the OTel collector. Acts as the metrics UI until Grafana is re-added.
- **OTel Collector** on host ports `14317` (gRPC) + `14318` (HTTP) + `13133` (health). Config at `docker/otel-collector/config.yaml`.
- **Grafana is not started** — dropped from `docker-compose.yml` after a local Docker TLS/corporate-proxy issue blocked the image pull. Provisioning files under `docker/grafana/provisioning/` are preserved so the service can be re-added as a single block once image pulls work.

Ports deliberately shifted into the 1xxxx range to avoid collisions with Optikk's own OTLP ingest (`4317`), the frontend dev server (`3000`), and ClickHouse (`9000`/`8123`).

